==Installation==
This application requires gDesklets core and shell to be installed
To install run gDesklets shell, select File - > Install package and search
for gDesklet archive (for e.g. Quote-0.1.tar.gz) - this will install
the desklet to your /home/[user name]/.gdesklets/Displays directory.

Then choose Quote of the Day gdesklet from "Misc" category

